822
00:39:21,382 --> 00:39:22,342
Thanks, Mike.

823
00:39:22,344 --> 00:39:25,900
♪ ♪

824
00:39:35,541 --> 00:39:37,431
So what do you think?

825
00:39:37,431 --> 00:39:39,481
