882
00:41:57,385 --> 00:41:58,889
effective immediately.

883
00:41:58,891 --> 00:42:01,773
I'm sorry, I don't understand.

884
00:42:01,773 --> 00:42:03,311
You created this position for me

885
00:42:03,311 --> 00:42:05,137
on the other side of the world.

886
00:42:05,137 --> 00:42:06,641
And we both know it
wasn't for my benefit

887
00:42:06,641 --> 00:42:08,563
or the company's.

888
00:42:08,565 --> 00:42:10,262
I don't know where do you
get your information...

889
00:42:10,262 --> 00:42:12,152
Don't patronize me.

890
00:42:12,152 --> 00:42:15,483
I also know that Billy and
Brooke are getting married.

891
00:42:15,485 --> 00:42:17,057
Is there anything
you wouldn't do for her?

892
00:42:17,983 --> 00:42:20,802
Look, Alison, I admit I
created the position for you,

893
00:42:20,802 --> 00:42:22,467
but it's not for
the reasons you think.

894
00:42:22,467 --> 00:42:24,260
I have an eye for talent,
you're a very...

