898
00:42:29,675 --> 00:42:33,197
♪ ♪

899
00:42:47,358 --> 00:42:50,208
♪ ♪

900
00:42:50,208 --> 00:42:53,539
Dr. Shaw.

901
00:42:53,539 --> 00:42:55,556
You have succeeded in completely

902
00:42:55,557 --> 00:42:57,382
destroying my attention span.

903
00:42:57,384 --> 00:42:59,048
And for that I get a rose?

904
00:42:59,050 --> 00:43:00,074
Yes.

