916
00:43:24,612 --> 00:43:26,885
I hope so.

917
00:43:26,887 --> 00:43:29,896
I'll pick you up about 7:00?

918
00:43:29,898 --> 00:43:31,532
Bring your toothbrush.

919
00:44:04,271 --> 00:44:05,231
♪ ♪

920
00:44:05,231 --> 00:44:07,472
Ohh...

921
00:44:07,474 --> 00:44:10,226
You are getting distracted.

922
00:44:10,228 --> 00:44:11,445
I can't take this.

923
00:44:14,007 --> 00:44:15,672
I swear to God, I'll kill myself

924
00:44:15,673 --> 00:44:16,889
