to get rid of you.

925
00:44:16,891 --> 00:44:20,447
♪ ♪

926
00:44:27,525 --> 00:44:29,960
Don't do anything you'll regret.

927
00:44:29,960 --> 00:44:31,081
I've tried suicide before.

928
00:44:31,081 --> 00:44:32,811
Don't think
I won't try it again.

929
00:44:32,813 --> 00:44:36,237
♪ ♪

930
00:44:36,239 --> 00:44:37,679
No!

931
00:44:37,681 --> 00:44:38,704
Kimberly!

932
00:44:38,706 --> 00:44:39,858
I'm sorry, if you die, I'm free,

933
00:44:39,858 --> 00:44:40,882
