934
00:44:40,884 --> 00:44:42,579
If we both die, good riddance!

935
00:44:42,581 --> 00:44:45,014
Kimberly! Kimberly, stop!

936
00:44:45,016 --> 00:44:46,585
♪ ♪

937
00:44:46,585 --> 00:44:49,275
No!

938
00:44:49,277 --> 00:44:53,025
♪ ♪

939
00:44:59,688 --> 00:45:01,353
I'm free.

940
00:45:01,353 --> 00:45:03,530
I'm free.

941
00:45:03,532 --> 00:45:06,862
