957
00:45:41,684 --> 00:45:43,829
Well, it better.

958
00:45:43,829 --> 00:45:46,103
'Cause if it doesn't, I'm gonna
hold you personally responsible

959
00:45:46,103 --> 00:45:48,251
for ruining the most
important day of my life.

960
00:45:51,068 --> 00:45:53,503
I certainly hope
that wasn't a client.

961
00:45:53,503 --> 00:45:55,425
Alison found out
about the wedding.

962
00:45:55,425 --> 00:45:56,963
Oh, right. Sorry about that.

963
00:45:56,963 --> 00:45:58,789
When she called for you
the other day,

964
00:45:58,789 --> 00:45:59,909
I assumed she already knew.

965
00:45:59,911 --> 00:46:02,184
You told her?
Well, inadvertently.

966
00:46:02,184 --> 00:46:04,938
But you don't have to worry, she's
not exactly on the guest list.

967
00:46:04,940 --> 00:46:06,509
Oh, here's the groom-to-be.

968
00:46:06,510 --> 00:46:08,108
24 hours and counting.

969
00:46:08,110 --> 00:46:10,353
Mmm.

970
00:46:10,353 --> 00:46:11,922
So, you ready to go?

971
00:46:11,923 --> 00:46:13,300
Yes, but I just
got off the phone

