00:46:14,679 --> 00:46:16,182
everything is
just going haywire.

974
00:46:16,184 --> 00:46:18,458
Would you mind terribly
staying at the house tonight?

975
00:46:18,458 --> 00:46:19,706
It would really help
keep us on schedule.

976
00:46:19,706 --> 00:46:20,666
Sure, why not?

977
00:46:20,668 --> 00:46:22,492
Okay.

978
00:46:22,494 --> 00:46:24,255
I'll make sure Daddy's chauffeur
picks up your things.

979
00:46:24,255 --> 00:46:25,217
Great.

980
00:46:26,563 --> 00:46:30,181
♪ ♪

