come home all night.

984
00:46:57,442 --> 00:46:59,235
Hey, I'm sorry.

985
00:46:59,237 --> 00:47:00,708
I should've called.

986
00:47:00,710 --> 00:47:02,568
Well, where'd you go
after you dropped me off?

987
00:47:02,568 --> 00:47:05,545
Nowhere, really.
