990
00:47:09,871 --> 00:47:11,280
I could've handled it better,

991
00:47:11,280 --> 00:47:14,130
but I'm just not
that good at this.

992
00:47:14,132 --> 00:47:16,277
All you have to do
is talk to me.

993
00:47:16,278 --> 00:47:17,976
I know!

994
00:47:17,976 --> 00:47:20,184
I know, but the whole
thing got under my skin.

995
00:47:20,186 --> 00:47:21,851
I mean, how do you sleep
in the same bed

996
00:47:21,851 --> 00:47:22,909
with somebody who just said no

997
00:47:22,909 --> 00:47:24,414
to your marriage proposal?

998
00:47:24,414 --> 00:47:26,110
I felt like an idiot, Jo.

999
00:47:26,112 --> 00:47:28,226
I didn't mean to hurt
you, I just... you threw me.

1000
00:47:28,226 --> 00:47:30,052
I mean, we never talked about
