1001
00:47:30,052 --> 00:47:31,909
I don't know
if I'm ready for one.

1002
00:47:31,911 --> 00:47:34,407
I shouldn't have
sprung it on you,

1003
00:47:34,409 --> 00:47:36,137
but I felt it, so I said it.

1004
00:47:36,139 --> 00:47:40,143
Hanson! I don't pay you
to stand around and talk.

1005
00:47:40,143 --> 00:47:42,608
Tell your girlfriend
she can't park on the site.

1006
00:47:42,608 --> 00:47:45,108
Yeah, all right.

1007
00:47:45,108 --> 00:47:46,934
I got to get back to work.

1008
00:47:46,934 --> 00:47:47,990
Am I gonna see you tonight?

1009
00:47:47,992 --> 00:47:49,784
Yeah.

1010
00:47:49,784 --> 00:47:52,858
Yeah, I'll come right home.

1011
00:47:52,860 --> 00:47:54,878
I did miss you, Jo.

1012
00:47:54,878 --> 00:47:56,577
I missed you, too.

1013
00:48:00,164 --> 00:48:04,039
♪ ♪

1014
00:48:13,873 --> 00:48:15,251
I'm sorry I missed
the breakfast meeting.

1015
00:48:15,251 --> 00:48:18,038
I overslept.

1016
00:48:18,039 --> 00:48:19,704
I'm not surprised.

1017
00:48:19,704 --> 00:48:22,586
Apparently you were
out quite late.

1018
00:48:22,588 --> 00:48:24,635
I had a working dinner
with Jane Mancini.

1019
00:48:24,637 --> 00:48:28,353
We went over some
sketches for the fall line.

1020
00:48:28,353 --> 00:48:31,106
I tried calling you
several times, Richard.

1021
00:48:31,108 --> 00:48:33,063
I gave up at 1:00.

1022
00:48:34,182 --> 00:48:36,297
We had a lot to cover.

1023
00:48:36,297 --> 00:48:38,369
Now, is there something else
that you'd like to discuss?

1024
00:48:39,853 --> 00:48:41,197
You slept with her, didn't you?

1025
00:48:41,199 --> 00:48:42,480
No.

1026
00:48:44,786 --> 00:48:46,291
Even if I did,

1027
00:48:46,293 --> 00:48:47,635
we agreed that it was okay
to see other people.

1028
00:48:47,637 --> 00:48:49,110
Do you remember that, Mackenzie?

1029
00:48:49,110 --> 00:48:51,480
Only because I didn't
want to lose you.

1030
00:48:51,481 --> 00:48:53,530
Richard, this is too painful.

1031
00:48:53,532 --> 00:48:55,934
I can't stand to think of
you with another woman.

1032
00:48:57,344 --> 00:48:59,744
You're gonna be
late for your meeting.

1033
00:48:59,746 --> 00:49:01,123
Richard, I love you.

1034
00:49:04,262 --> 00:49:06,056
Look, I, uh...

1035
00:49:06,056 --> 00:49:09,420
I know I'm not as young as Jane,

1036
00:49:09,420 --> 00:49:12,559
